Dia pasti akan pergi
ke rumah Tuhan.

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:46.120
Kakek, Bibi, dan Sanju
sedang mencari di sini.

00:16:47.400 --> 00:16:49.000
Jangan berbalik, Bibi.

00:16:49.080 --> 00:16:50.360
Lihat saja ke depan, oke?

00:16:50.440 --> 00:16:54.240
Nona Sukhwinder dan
